    Each OWLOntology contains a reference to its manager. This method is no longer necessary. Parsers will obtain the manager from the ontology in the various parse methods i.e. OWLParser.parse(OWLOntologyDocumentSource, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntology) , OWLParser.parse(OWLOntologyDocumentSource, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntology) , OWLParser.parse(OWLOntologyDocumentSource, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntology, org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyLoaderConfiguration)
